definition: being one more than one, one of the four playing cards in a deck that have two spots
details:
adjective
- being one more than one
= example: being one more than one
= synonyms: ii
noun
- one of the four playing cards in a deck that have two spots
= synonyms: deuce
- the cardinal number that is the sum of one and one or a numeral representing this number
= synonyms: deuce
